{"tid":2407091,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深、夜、放、煙、花、死、全、家！","createTime":"2021-02-13T17:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T05:01:37.000Z","uid":211994,"like":56,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"351d2273a4e058c1b764174d31ee375cbc075b1a","tid":2407091,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"重點係「深夜」放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你8點9點放都算，雖然我淨係聽到爆炸聲乜柒煙花都欣賞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講我以為出面放緊tg<br />\n<br />\n你12點幾一點放煙花，即係幫你老母搵多啲恩客啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你自己爽一陣，其他人就一啲都唔爽，瞓瞓下俾你班仆街嚇醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次建議咁多位想深夜嘈鳩人嘅仆街們<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺舊煙花落口，點火，等佢就爆炸個下先攞出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠哂刺激夠哂爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa8baf05c3417a323d484bb87bbabc52d6b201e","tid":2407091,"uid":370878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"正話聽到有人放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到個個開晒窗廉睇咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51c208add7cbbfdf947cfff46f1a223a3ee922f","tid":2407091,"uid":37540,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"我想講 家中主子都俾啲深夜煙花嚇到驚咗成晚<br />\n可想而知 啲流浪貓狗可能仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de4336ee6de0aeea7a23beb03474298a17d67b8","tid":2407091,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f51c208add7cbbfdf947cfff46f1a223a3ee922f","tid":2407091,"uid":37540,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"我想講 家中主子都俾啲深夜煙花嚇到驚咗成晚<br />\n可想而知 啲流浪貓狗可能仲驚<img src=